        <div class="parva-badge" style="background:rgba(107,26,26,0.1);color:#aaa;">👑 PREMIUM · ★ LETTING GO</div>
        <div class="parva-title" data-lang="en">Ashramavasika Parva — The Forest Retirement</div>
        <div class="parva-title" data-lang="hi" style="display:none">Ashramavasika Parva — The Forest Retirement</div>
